  "html": "\u003cdiv id=\"readability-page-1\" class=\"page\"\u003e\u003cdiv id=\"jump-content\" tabindex=\"-1\"\u003e\n            \n\n    \n    \n\n    \u003carticle\u003e\n\n    \n    \n\n\n\n\n\n    \n\n    \n      \n\n\u003cdiv data-analytics-module=\"{\n    \u0026#34;module_name\u0026#34;: \u0026#34;Hero Menu\u0026#34;,\n    \u0026#34;section_header\u0026#34;: \u0026#34;New in Gemini: Gemini Live and connected Google apps in more languages\u0026#34;\n  }\"\u003e\n  \u003cdiv\u003e\n      \u003cdiv\u003e\n          \u003cp\u003eOct 03, 2024\u003c/p\u003e\n          \n            \u003cp data-reading-time-render=\"\"\u003e[[read-time]] min read\u003c/p\u003e\n          \n        \u003c/div\u003e\n      \n        \u003cp\u003e\n          Gemini Live is expanding its capabilities. In the coming weeks, you’ll be able to converse with Gemini and have it perform actions on your behalf in your preferred language.\n        \u003c/p\u003e\n      \n    \u003c/div\u003e\n  \u003cdiv data-summary-id=\"ai_summary_1\" data-component=\"uni-ai-generated-summary\" data-analytics-module=\"{\n    \u0026#34;event\u0026#34;: \u0026#34;module_impression\u0026#34;,\n    \u0026#34;module_name\u0026#34;: \u0026#34;ai_summary\u0026#34;,\n    \u0026#34;section_header\u0026#34;: \u0026#34;CTA\u0026#34;\n  }\"\u003e\n          \u003ch2\u003eGeneral summary\u003c/h2\u003e\n          \u003cp\u003eGemini, your personal AI assistant, is expanding its horizons! Gemini Live, which allows for natural conversations, will now support over 40 languages, enabling more people to engage in different languages on the same device. Additionally, Gemini will connect to more Google apps in various languages, making it easier to access information and complete tasks across your favorite Google services. With Gemini Live, you can brainstorm ideas, explore new topics, and even practice presentations. Connect Gemini to apps like Gmail, Maps, and YouTube to enhance your productivity. Gemini is committed to making AI accessible to everyone, and these updates bring the power of AI to a wider audience.\u003c/p\u003e\n          \n          \u003cp\u003e\u003csmall\u003e\n            Summaries were generated by Google AI. Generative AI is experimental.\n          \u003c/small\u003e\n        \u003c/p\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\n\u003c/div\u003e\n\n    \n\n    \n      \u003cdiv\u003e\n      \u003cp\u003e\n        \u003cvideo autoplay=\"\" muted=\"\" loop=\"\" playsinline=\"\" src=\"https://storage.googleapis.com/gweb-uniblog-publish-prod/original_videos/Gemini_Live_from_IO_Global_v05.mp4\" title=\"Animation of Gemini logo and smartphone with text: Go Live to talk things out with Gemini\" poster=\"\n            \n              https://storage.googleapis.com/gweb-uniblog-publish-prod/original_images/Gemini_Live_Global_Static.png\n            \"\u003e\n          Sorry, your browser doesn\u0026#39;t support embedded videos, but don\u0026#39;t worry, you can\n            \u003ca href=\"https://storage.googleapis.com/gweb-uniblog-publish-prod/original_videos/Gemini_Live_from_IO_Global_v05.mp4\"\u003edownload it\u003c/a\u003e\n            and watch it with your favorite video player!\n        \u003c/video\u003e\n      \u003c/p\u003e\n      \n    \u003c/div\u003e\n\n    \n\n    \n    \u003cdiv data-reading-time=\"true\" data-component=\"uni-drop-cap|uni-tombstone\"\u003e\n\n            \n              \n\n\n\u003cgoogle-read-aloud-player data-analytics-module=\"{\n        \u0026#34;event\u0026#34;: \u0026#34;module_impression\u0026#34;,\n        \u0026#34;module_name\u0026#34;: \u0026#34;ai_audio\u0026#34;,\n        \u0026#34;section_header\u0026#34;: \u0026#34;New in Gemini: Gemini Live and connected Google apps in more languages\u0026#34;\n    }\" data-date-modified=\"2024-10-03T13:00:00.235957+00:00\" data-progress-bar-style=\"half-wave\" data-api-key=\"AIzaSyBLT6VkYe-x7sWLZI2Ep26-fNkBKgND-Ac\" data-article-style=\"style9\" data-tracking-ids=\"G-HGNBTNCHCQ,G-6NKTLKV14N\" data-voice-list=\"en.ioh-pngnat:Cyan,en.usb-pngnat:Lime\" data-layout-style=\"style1\" data-highlight-mode=\"word-over-paragraph\" data-highlight-text-color=\"#000000\" data-highlight-word-background=\"#8AB4F8\" data-highlight-paragraph-background=\"#D2E3FC\" data-background=\"linear-gradient(180deg, #F1F3F4 0%, #F8F9FA 100%)\" data-foreground-color=\"#202124\" data-font=\"600 16px Google Sans, sans-serif\" data-box-shadow=\"0px 1px 3px 1px rgba(60, 64, 67, 0.15)\"\u003e\n\u003c/google-read-aloud-player\u003e\n\n\n\n\n            \n\n            \n            \n\n\n  \n    \u003cdiv data-component=\"uni-article-paragraph\" data-analytics-module=\"{\n           \u0026#34;module_name\u0026#34;: \u0026#34;Paragraph\u0026#34;,\n           \u0026#34;section_header\u0026#34;: \u0026#34;New in Gemini: Gemini Live and connected Google apps in more languages\u0026#34;\n         }\"\u003e\u003cp data-block-key=\"xjhk6\"\u003eGemini is designed to be your personal AI assistant — one that’s conversational, intuitive and helpful. To make it even more accessible and useful, we’re expanding Gemini Live to more languages, allowing you to have natural conversations in different languages. Furthermore, Gemini will be able to connect to more Google apps in different languages, making it easier to access information and complete tasks across your favorite Google services.\u003c/p\u003e\u003ch2 data-block-key=\"9q6gq\"\u003eGemini Live: Now speaking your language\u003c/h2\u003e\u003cp data-block-key=\"8ha1\"\u003eAt Made by Google this year, we \u003ca href=\"https://blog.google/products/gemini/made-by-google-gemini-ai-updates/\"\u003eintroduced\u003c/a\u003e Gemini Live, allowing people to have free-flowing, natural conversations with Gemini in English. Starting today and rolling out over the coming weeks, we’re expanding Gemini Live on Android phones to more than 40 languages, so more people can chat, collaborate and experience conversational AI in different languages.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp data-block-key=\"70npr\"\u003eGemini Live will support conversations in up to two languages on the same device, and we plan to expand to more languages in the future. You can easily set your preferred languages in the Google app:\u003c/p\u003e\u003col\u003e\u003cli data-block-key=\"sgg0\"\u003eOn your Android phone or tablet, open the Google app and at the top, tap your profile picture or initial.\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli data-block-key=\"tdl2\"\u003eTap Settings \u0026gt; Google Assistant \u0026gt; Languages.\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli data-block-key=\"8p3kb\"\u003eChoose a \u003ca href=\"https://support.google.com/gemini/answer/15274899#supported_languages\"\u003esupported language\u003c/a\u003e.\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli data-block-key=\"5ius7\"\u003eOptionally, you can add a second supported language. For now, you can set and use up to two languages with Gemini Live.\u003c/li\u003e\u003c/ol\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\n  \n\n  \n    \n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n  \n      \u003cdiv data-analytics-module=\"{\n          \u0026#34;module_name\u0026#34;: \u0026#34;Inline Images\u0026#34;,\n          \u0026#34;section_header\u0026#34;: \u0026#34;New in Gemini: Gemini Live and connected Google apps in more languages\u0026#34;\n        }\"\u003e\n  \n\n  \u003cp\u003e\n\n      \n      \n        \n          \u003cvideo tabindex=\"0\" autoplay=\"\" loop=\"\" muted=\"\" playsinline=\"\" src=\"https://storage.googleapis.com/gweb-uniblog-publish-prod/original_videos/Selecting_a_second_language.mp4\" type=\"video/mp4\" title=\"Animation of a user selecting French as a second language\" alt=\"Gemini Live, selecting a second language\"\u003e\n            Video format not supported\n          \u003c/video\u003e\n        \n      \n    \n    \u003c/p\u003e\n    \n  \n    \u003c/div\u003e\n  \n\n\n\n  \n\n  \n    \u003cdiv data-component=\"uni-article-paragraph\" data-analytics-module=\"{\n           \u0026#34;module_name\u0026#34;: \u0026#34;Paragraph\u0026#34;,\n           \u0026#34;section_header\u0026#34;: \u0026#34;New in Gemini: Gemini Live and connected Google apps in more languages\u0026#34;\n         }\"\u003e\u003ch2 data-block-key=\"vqfj0\"\u003eYour conversational AI partner\u003c/h2\u003e\u003cp data-block-key=\"d96d1\"\u003eGemini Live is truly conversational. It’s like having a chat with a friend: you can brainstorm ideas, explore new topics or even practice for a big presentation. Gemini Live can keep up with your conversations so you can interrupt, change direction or dive deeper on a particular subject. And with 10 distinct voices to choose from, you can customize your experience and find the perfect tone and style for your conversation.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp data-block-key=\"5ij6t\"\u003eHere are just a few examples of what you can do with Gemini Live:\u003c/p\u003e\u003cul\u003e\u003cli data-block-key=\"29n71\"\u003e\u003cb\u003eAsk for advice:\u003c/b\u003e Brainstorm with Gemini on a range of topics, such as potential jobs that are well-suited to your skillset or degree.\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli data-block-key=\"74lc2\"\u003e\u003cb\u003ePlan for an event:\u003c/b\u003e Chat with Gemini about hosting a birthday party for friends and family.\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli data-block-key=\"3cd6\"\u003e\u003cb\u003eDive into new subjects and expand your horizons:\u003c/b\u003e Ask Gemini Live about historical events, scientific concepts or even the rules of a game like chess or mahjong\u003cb\u003e.\u003c/b\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli data-block-key=\"e0hgn\"\u003e\u003cb\u003eExplore new local topics and ideas:\u003c/b\u003e Chat with Gemini about topics specific to your region or interests.\u003c/li\u003e\u003c/ul\u003e\u003ch2 data-block-key=\"3vnl\"\u003eYour favorite apps, now connected with Gemini\u003c/h2\u003e\u003cp data-block-key=\"bm5ps\"\u003eSince we brought \u003ca href=\"https://support.google.com/gemini/answer/13695044\"\u003eExtensions\u003c/a\u003e directly into Gemini, people have been getting more things done with apps and services they already use like Gmail, Maps and YouTube. We \u003ca href=\"https://blog.google/products/gemini/made-by-google-gemini-ai-updates/\"\u003erecently\u003c/a\u003e announced we’re expanding the capability to connect even more Google tools in English, including Google Calendar, Tasks, Keep and Utilities. With Extensions, Gemini can pull together what you need from other apps and services to help you get things done across them easier and faster.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp data-block-key=\"8od12\"\u003eOver the coming weeks, you\u0026#39;ll be able to connect to new tools across different apps and in more languages, making it even easier to get things done. Here are a few examples of how you can use Gemini extensions in your language:\u003c/p\u003e\u003cul\u003e\u003cli data-block-key=\"8vnu3\"\u003eHave Gemini dig out that lasagna recipe sent to you in your Gmail, and ask it to add the ingredients to your shopping list in Keep.\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli data-block-key=\"3bjcq\"\u003eSnap a photo of a concert flier and ask Gemini if you\u0026#39;re free that day — and even set a reminder to buy tickets.\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli data-block-key=\"7cuqd\"\u003eAsk Gemini when your favorite comic book movie is next out and then ask it to remind you a week before to buy tickets for it.\u003c/li\u003e\u003c/ul\u003e\u003ch2 data-block-key=\"5vv10\"\u003eA world of possibilities, in your language\u003c/h2\u003e\u003cp data-block-key=\"daodv\"\u003eWe believe everyone should have access to the power of AI. By expanding Gemini Live and app connections to more languages, we\u0026#39;re making this a reality, helping people worldwide connect with information and experience the benefits of an AI-powered assistant.\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\n  \n\n\n            \n            \n\n            \n              \n\n\n\n\n            \n          \u003c/div\u003e\n  \u003c/article\u003e\n  \n\n\n\n\n\n\n  \n\n  \n\n\n\u003cdiv data-component=\"uni-related-articles\" data-analytics-module=\"{\n    \u0026#34;module_